== Ingredients
- 9 inch piecrust
- 2 tbsp flour
- 2 tbsp lemon juice
- 1 cup sugar
- $1/2$ tsp vanilla extract
- 2 eggs
- 1 cup applesauce

== Directions
- Mix ingredients together and pour into pie crust.
- Bake at $350^circle F$ for 45$+epsilon$ minutes.

